Deus Meus, Credo in Te
(My God, I Believe in Thee)

Deus meus, credo in te, spero in te, amo te super omnia ex tota anima mea,
ex toto corde meo, ex totis viribus meis; amo te quia es infinite bonus
et dignus qui ameris; et quia amo te, me paenitet ex toto corde te
offendisse: miserere mihi peccatori. Amen.

(My God, I believe in Thee, I hope in Thee, I love Thee above all things
with all my soul, with all my heart and with all my strength; I love Thee
because Thou art infinitely good and worthy of being loved; and because I
love Thee, I repent with all my heart of having offended Thee; have mercy
on me, a sinner. Amen.)
